{"title":"DF Paraphernalia: T-Shirts and Hoodies Are Back","link":"https://store.daringfireball.net/","date":1776721080000,"content":"\n<p><a href=\"https://store.daringfireball.net/\">\n<img src=\"https://daringfireball.net/members/images/2024/classic-976.png\" alt=\"Thumbnail of a classic Daring Fireball logo t-shirt.\" height=\"445\" width=\"445\" />\n</a></p>\n\n<p>Daring Fireball t-shirts and hoodies are back. Order now, and we’ll start printing shirts at the end of this week and shipping them out next week. Go ahead and place your order now, while I gather my thoughts about <a href=\"https://daringfireball.net/linked/2026/04/20/cook-community-letter\">today’s</a> Apple leadership <a href=\"https://daringfireball.net/linked/2026/04/20/cook-chairman-ternus-ceo\">news</a>.</p>\n\n<div>\n<a href=\"https://daringfireball.net/linked/2026/04/20/df-t-shirts-and-hoodies\"> ★ </a>\n</div>\n\n\t","author":"John Gruber","siteTitle":"Daring Fireball","siteHash":"fc569638025dadf22a867470f8215f38855cf50e975782a6c989909474292a36","entryHash":"643f699961aabf2e76fdbdf9e5b61318a55763fe45271a3e5ee379a414bbdffc","category":"Tech"}